  "_comment": "Index hub lists ~50 provider-type manuals A-Z, each at /lists/<type>-manual-for-masshealth-providers. Every manual = shared Subch 1-3/5 (all-provider regs+billing) + type-specific Subch 4 (130 CMR coverage regs) + Subch 6 (service codes/PA tables) + shared Appendices A-Z. Each /doc/ slug has TWO download variants (PDF + DOCX), suffix→format mapping is inconsistent (-0 usually PDF but not always) — fetch handler should HEAD content-type and prefer application/pdf. Pharmacy has no Subchapter 6 (drug list is separate at mass.gov/druglist). NEMT brokered (PT-1) policy lives in TRN regs.",
